Text: Do you have the first volume of Ms. Marvel? What about the Ant-Man issues of Tales to Astonish?
STFmaryville by any chance do you have Man Things' appearances on Adventure into Fear??

gpack3, derav, i don't have any of those. if you're looking for a lot of great scans of classic marvel issues, i highly recommend that you Google "H33t" -- on the H33t site, search for "marvel chronology"... PeteThePIPster has compiled everything published from 1939-2011, ordered by cover dates.
